                                            States</hi>, <hi rend="italic">London,</hi></placeName>
                                    <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-07-23"><hi rend="italic">July</hi> 23, 1868.</date></dateline></opener>
                            <p>Mr. Moran, chargé d’affaires of the United States at London, presents
                                his compliments to —————— ——————, and has the honor to transmit
                                herewith a letter from the Department of State at Washington city.
                                He begs to say that the volume to which it refers will be sent
                                through the channel named in the memorandum below.</p>
                            <p>Mr. Moran will be pleased to receive and forward to his government an
                                acknowledgment of the reception of the letter and volume in
                                question.</p>
